requirement:
During the roll-to-level segment, transition to the landing rollout segment when one of the following conditions is met, with a softening time limit set to 2s.
1) The landing gear fully compressed signal is true for 12 consecutive steps;
2) The remote control grounding signal is true;
3) The cumulative count of 75 steps indicates that the remote control signal status is abnormal. Note that this condition only needs to be judged once.
